msgstr ""

#: ../../source/ProfilingTest_prof.inc:5
msgid "Information"
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/ProfilingTest_prof.inc:7
msgid ""
"All times are measured using a real-time wall clock. This means context "
"switching produces bad worst-case execution times (max times) for blocks."
" If you want better results, use a CPU-time clock or run the command "
"using real-time priviliges (avoiding context switches)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/ProfilingTest_prof.inc:12
msgid ""
"Note that for blocks where the individual execution time is close to the "
"accuracy of the real-time clock, the maximum measured time may deviate a "
"lot from the average."
msgstr ""

#: ../../source/ProfilingTest_prof.inc:16
msgid ""
"For more details, see `ProfilingTest\\_prof.xml "
"<ProfilingTest_prof.xml>`__."
msgstr ""

